{"tid":1319119,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"人人都可以係記者","createTime":"2019-07-15T05:46:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T06:02:27.000Z","uid":193387,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b9aa0dc5da68f1c94abe15352afeaf8d982df522","tid":1319119,"uid":193387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T05:46:09.000Z","msg":"唔知有無得諗。<br />\n各位巴絲，特別係傳媒界人仕歡迎俾意見。<br />\n<br />\n有無諗過其實人人都可以係記者。<br />\n申請記者證成本有限，俾$50 入會記協再加$50 申請記者證。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkja.org.hk/apply-membership/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkja.org.hk%2Fapply-membership%2F&d=Nl%2Bce6%2FxXxAB2W4e8qnvdiYtkWzW%2FBkyQE6eFpzr100%3D&h=b7af5427\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkja.org.hk/apply-membership/</a><br />\n最難攪只係要有傳媒認你係員工。<br />\n如果攪個小眾籌起間網媒公司起個blog，各位登記成為呢間網媒嘅記者，各位巴絲再出篇blog 證明自己係自由撰稿人。咁就可以去申請記者證。<br />\n<br />\n成為記者可以收集黑材料留底等投訴，而且有人對傳媒係最客氣，俾人扑都細力啲，都容易啲全身而退。啱哂啲想做啲嘢又怕衝太前嘅巴絲。<br />\n<br />\n但有無行內人知入會同申請記者證嚴唔嚴？<br />\n有咩諗漏歡迎任插。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9113cba254224f59a8b41d95ff78783e6a45f888","tid":1319119,"uid":61520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T05:46:36.000Z","msg":"港共期待緊死第一個警察或者示威者<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1318968\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1318968</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1208bc4ebd708bbaf35fd494703900d5e494d3e0","tid":1319119,"uid":706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T05:47:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔好亂咁認記者，結果只會令真正既記者做唔到野<br />\n麻煩唔好做豬隊友</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">請唔好再叫狗/黑警，係懷疑冒警暴徒</span><br />\n<br />\n最低成本既方法，又減低傷亡，和理非都可以幫手<br />\n請幫手推！！<br />\n<br />\n警告你地唔好再屌警察老母<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1317630\" target=\